des: WNXC-DB on Live365 offers Full Spectrum Listening from the heart of North Carolina. Weekdays 6am-10pm feature alternative, modern, and classics from the Radio Free Raleigh rock n' roll archive. Sunday-Thursday overnights 10pm-6am experience The Ultraviolet NXC, a chill mix of post-rock, ambient, experimental, and contemporary ensemble tracks . Weekends from Friday night at 10pm through Sunday evening at 10pm relax with legendary blues, soulful favorites, jazz, and reggae. (All times Eastern, US)
